page.title: 20THE LAST WORD
page.content: This Survey has been prepared under the auspices of Croughton WI, and the material put together by Ann Sharman and Pamela Bennett. David Bennett provided the item on the Parish Council. Statistics were provided by Alan Hawkins, Headmaster and Clerk to the Parish Council, and statistics and information by SSgt Cathy L Henderson, USAF, the Unit Public Affairs Representative of 2130th Information Systems Squadron. Members of the WI approved the text, and made some suggestions for alteration.
